{"lastModified":1771253512514,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nPresenting the Nautitech 46 Fly – Sithonia, a modern 6-cabin catamaran meticulously constructed in 2019, now anchored at Marina Alimos, Greece. Sithonia comfortably accommodates up to 10 guests across four double cabins with ensuite WC and two single cabins for the crew, ensuring a cozy retreat for all. Rest easy knowing that pillows and blankets are included for your convenience.\n\nEquipped with a classic mainsail, electric winches, solar panels, and a generator, Sithonia offers both performance and sustainability. Navigate with ease using the salon GPS plotter and stay comfortable with features like heating and air conditioning. Entertainment options abound with an audio system and outside speakers.\n\nIn the fully-equipped galley, you’ll find everything you need to prepare delicious meals, including an oven, cooker, sink, and kitchen utensils","blueprint":{"name":"SITHONIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::b4385230-37df-11f0-834e-8b715c579399/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::b4073010-37df-11f0-834e-8b715c579399/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::b438ee70-37df-11f0-834e-8b715c579399/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::b4391580-37df-11f0-834e-8b715c579399/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::b407cc51-37df-11f0-834e-8b715c579399/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::b43ac330-37df-11f0-834e-8b715c579399/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::facfe720-37db-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::b403d4b0-37df-11f0-834e-8b715c579399/{imageVariant}"